  "cscw_dialogue": [
    {
      "turn_id": 1,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "我想画一个GitHub Actions的工作流程图，展示开发者怎么触发不同的自动化任务。核心角色有三个：开发者、GitHub平台本身，还有执行任务的Runner。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dev",
        "GitHub",
        "Runner"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 2,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白了，用sequenceDiagram。开发者是actor，GitHub和Runner是participant。那开发者到GitHub的交互怎么描述？是推送代码吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dev",
        "GitHub"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，开发者会触发各种workflow。我们列四个典型的：Build构建、Docs文档生成、Issue Watcher问题监控，还有一个Codebase Mindmap代码库导图。每个都是Dev指向GitHub的triggers动作。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dev",
        "GitHub",
        "Build",
        "Docs",
        "Issue Watcher",
        "Codebase Mindmap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "好，我先画出第一条线：Dev触发Build，然后GitHub派发给Runner执行。我用loop框把Build包起来表示这是一个循环执行的过程。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dev",
        "GitHub",
        "Runner",
        "Build",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "Build那条看起来对。继续把Docs加上，同样是Dev触发、GitHub dispatch到Runner的模式。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dev",
        "GitHub",
        "Runner",
        "Docs"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 6,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "Docs也画好了。接下来是Issue Watcher和Codebase Mindmap对吧？这两个也是同样的触发链路。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Dev",
        "GitHub",
        "Runner",
        "Issue Watcher",
        "Codebase Mindmap"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 7,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "repair",
      "utterance": "等等，Issue Watcher那个我确认一下——应该是持续监控的，所以loop框是对的。但Codebase Mindmap我想改成定期触发，不是每次推送都跑。不过loop也能表达周期性，就这样吧，不用改。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Issue Watcher",
        "Codebase Mindmap",
        "loop"
      ],
      "is_repair": true
    },
    {
