      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "全部完成了。四条并行的workflow：Build、Docs、Issue Watcher、Codebase Mindmap，都是Dev→GitHub triggers，然后GitHub→Runner dispatch，各自有loop表示执行过程。结构清晰吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
